    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一而再，再而三地死去</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/7882bedf55e6e7ca36a2c43a2deaba91.poster.avif?t=1770287610\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/7882bedf55e6e7ca36a2c43a2deaba91.webm?t=1770287610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/7882bedf55e6e7ca36a2c43a2deaba91.mp4?t=1770287610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演一名由私人军事公司派遣的监察员，<br>前往调查 <strong>Underdog Corp.</strong> —— 一座早已被非法人体实验摧毁的废弃研究设施。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这座设施中，<br>你将遭遇那些被暴力机械义肢改造过的实验体 ——<br>而你自己，也会在战斗中失去身体的一部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了活下去，<br>你必须从他们的尸体上撕下义肢，<br>并将其强行移植到自己身上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次替换，都会让你变得更强……<br>但也会让你离人类越来越远。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持人性，<br>或成为你所恐惧的存在。<br>选择，掌握在你手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>激烈的战斗系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/a0d3e6f236563b3655bd9025e7ab610e.poster.avif?t=1770287610\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/a0d3e6f236563b3655bd9025e7ab610e.webm?t=1770287610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/a0d3e6f236563b3655bd9025e7ab610e.mp4?t=1770287610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你所谓的“自卫武器”，<br>可以在精确射击武器与残酷的近战棍之间自由切换。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把握时机精准格挡敌人攻击，<br>并用毁灭性的反击将其击溃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>更加冷酷</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/a5a465106ae73f917331bcf03ba4c36c.poster.avif?t=1770287610\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/a5a465106ae73f917331bcf03ba4c36c.webm?t=1770287610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/a5a465106ae73f917331bcf03ba4c36c.mp4?t=1770287610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个残暴而无情的实验室，<br>不会欢迎任何闯入者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但你别无选择，必须继续前进。<br>在每一次面对危险时，<br>你都将被迫做出关键抉择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扭曲的 2.5D 视觉美学</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/1b18dcd0a8b700dbdc1f912b70e03756.poster.avif?t=1770287610\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/1b18dcd0a8b700dbdc1f912b70e03756.webm?t=1770287610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164230/extras/1b18dcd0a8b700dbdc1f912b70e03756.mp4?t=1770287610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索这个黑暗的科幻恐怖世界 ——<br>它融合了粗粝的 3D 模型与像素风格的美术设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >锐利的光影与手工打造的环境，<br>共同营造出一个令人不安的 PS2 时代美学。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
